主要翻译
 
convert [sth] # vtr (change)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 转变 zhuǎn biàn TC Traditional Chinese 轉變  
 -- The senator's powerful speech converted public opinion.
 -- 议员慷慨激昂的演讲让公众观点发生了改变。
 
convert [sth] to [sth] vtr + prep (change to else)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 将…转换为  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 将…转化为 
 -- Please convert the fractions to decimals.
 -- 请将分数转化为小数。
 
convert [sth] into [sth] vtr + prep (transform, adapt)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 将…改造为  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 将…改建为 
 -- Mack converted the mailbox into a birdhouse.
 -- 马克将信箱改造成了鸟窝。
 
convert [sth] into [sth], convert [sth] to [sth] vtr + prep (currency: exchange)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 将…兑换为  (货币)
 -- I need to convert my US dollars into pounds sterling.
 -- 我需要将我的美元兑换为英镑。
 
convert [sb] # vtr informal (persuade)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 改变 gǎi biàn TC Traditional Chinese 改變  (信仰、党派或意见等)
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 说动 
 -- I know you feel strongly about it, but you'll never convert me.
 -- 我明白，你对这件事有很强的感情，但你是无法说动我的。
 
convert [sb] to [sth] vtr + prep (change 's mind)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 使…转而接受  
 -- Luke converted Sheila to the merits of jogging every morning.
 -- 卢克使茜拉转而接受每天早晨慢跑的好习惯。
 
convert # vi (change religion)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 改变宗教信仰  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 皈依 guī yī 
 -- After Judy converted, her new church community welcomed her.
 -- 朱迪皈依后受到了新教堂社群的欢迎。
 
convert to [sth] vi + prep (change to new religion)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 皈依 guī yī  
 -- Incredibly, Pope Pius II once considered converting to Islam.
 -- 令人惊奇的是，教皇皮乌斯二世曾一度考虑过皈依伊斯兰教。

其他翻译
 
convert n informal (person: newly convinced)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 改变信念 gǎi biàn xìn niàn TC Traditional Chinese 改變信念  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 改用 
 -- Joan is a recent convert to the Atkins diet.
 
convert n (person: adopts a religion)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 改变信仰 gǎi biàn xìn yǎng TC Traditional Chinese 改變信仰  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 皈依 gǎi biàn xìn yǎng，guī yī 
 -- Halley is a Christian convert.
 
convert vi (rugby: goal kick)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 踢定位球后得分  (英式橄榄球)
 -- The player converted with a drop kick.
 
convert vi informal (change your mind)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 改主意  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 改变看法 gǎi biàn kàn fǎ 
 -- I have never been a wine drinker, but this Chardonnay is so nice, I could be persuaded to convert!
 
convert into [sth] vi + prep (change to different form)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 转变为 TC Traditional Chinese 轉變為  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 转化为 
 -- This sofa converts into a bed.
 
convert [sth] # vtr (measure: find equivalent)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 换算 huàn suàn TC Traditional Chinese 換算  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 转换 huàn suàn，zhuǎn huàn TC Traditional Chinese 轉換 
 
convert [sth] vtr (currency: exchange)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 兑换 duì huàn TC Traditional Chinese 兌換  (货币)
 -- I need to convert some yen.
 
convert [sb] # vtr (make change religion)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 使...改变宗教信仰  
 -- The missionaries intended to convert as many people as possible.
 
convert [sth] into [sth] # vtr (measure: find equivalent)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 将…换算为  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 将…折合为 
 
convert [sth] into [sth], convert [sth] to [sth] vtr + prep (change over)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 改换 gǎi huàn  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 转换 gǎi huàn，zhuǎn huàn TC Traditional Chinese 轉換 
 -- Do you know the formula to convert inches to centimeters?
 -- 你知道英寸转厘米的公式吗？
 
convert [sb] to [sth] vtr + prep (make adopt new religion)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 使...接受新宗教信仰  
 -- Because she was worried about my soul, she kept trying to convert me to her religion.
 
convert [sth] to [sth] vtr + prep (building: modify, repurpose)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 改造，改建，改装 gǎi zào，gǎi jiàn，gǎi zhuāng TC Traditional Chinese 改造，改建，改裝  (建筑物)
 -- The old gas station has been converted to a diner.

